#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.sort_index.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.sort\\_index"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_index.sort_index:1 of
msgid "Sort object by labels (along an axis)."
msgstr "按标签（沿轴）排序对象。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.sort_index.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_index.sort_index:5 of
msgid ""
"The axis along which to sort.  The value 0 identifies the rows, and 1 "
"identifies the columns."
msgstr "排序的轴。值 0 表示行，1 表示列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_index.sort_index:8 of
msgid "If not None, sort on values in specified index level(s)."
msgstr "如果不为 None，则在指定的索引级别上排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_index.sort_index:10 of
msgid "Sort ascending vs. descending."
msgstr "升序或降序排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_index.sort_index:12 of
msgid "If True, perform operation in-place."
msgstr "如果为 True，则就地执行操作。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_index.sort_index:14 of
msgid ""
"Choice of sorting algorithm. See also ndarray.np.sort for more "
"information.  `mergesort` is the only stable algorithm. For DataFrames, "
"this option is only applied when sorting on a single column or label."
msgstr ""
"排序算法的选择。更多信息请参见 ndarray.np.sort。`mergesort` 是唯一的稳定"
"算法。对于 DataFrame，此选项仅在按单个列或标签排序时应用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_index.sort_index:19 of
msgid ""
"Puts NaNs at the beginning if `first`; `last` puts NaNs at the end. Not "
"implemented for MultiIndex."
msgstr ""
"如果为 `first`，则将 NaN 放在开头；`last` 将 NaN 放在末尾。对于 "
"MultiIndex 未实现。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_index.sort_index:22 of
msgid ""
"If True and sorting by level and index is multilevel, sort by other "
"levels too (in order) after sorting by specified level."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True 且索引是多级的，在按指定级别排序后，也会按其他级别（顺序）"
"排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_index.sort_index:25 of
msgid "If True, the resulting axis will be labeled 0, 1, …, n - 1."
msgstr "如果为 True，结果轴将被标记为 0, 1, …, n - 1。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_index.sort_index:27 of
msgid ""
"Parallel sorting algorithm, for the details, refer to: "
"http://csweb.cs.wfu.edu/bigiron/LittleFE-"
"PSRS/build/html/PSRSalgorithm.html"
msgstr ""
"并行排序算法，详情请参见：http://csweb.cs.wfu.edu/bigiron/LittleFE-PSRS/"
"build/html/PSRSalgorithm.html"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.sort_index.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.sort_index.sort_index:33 of
msgid ""
"**sorted_obj** -- DataFrame with sorted index if inplace=False, None "
"otherwise."
msgstr ""
"**sorted_obj** -- 如果 inplace=False，返回索引已排序的 DataFrame，否则"
"返回 None。"

